      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is currently not in running order. It has significant mechanical issues, most notably a failed engine that will require a complete overhaul or replacement to get back on the road. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable dents, fading paint, and some surface rust on the lower panels. Inside, the upholstery is heavily worn with tears in the driver's seat and a cracked dashboard. This is strictly a project car for someone with the tools and time to restore it, or it could serve as a valuable source for parts. It will need to be towed from its current location.",
