      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014seriously, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied it since day one, kept it garaged, and kept up with every single service. It\u2019s spotless inside and out. You won't find another one this clean! Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
