    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Presenting an exceptional 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera 4S, a definitive example of the 996.2 widebody aesthetic. This specimen is powered by a mid-mounted 3.6L flat-six engine delivering linear power through a 6-speed manual transaxle and a sophisticated all-wheel-drive system. Mechanical integrity is paramount; the M96 powerplant has received a documented LN Engineering IMS bearing retrofit, alongside a preventative rear main seal replacement. The chassis retains its factory-tuned damping, paired with 'Big Red' four-piston monobloc calipers and cross-drilled rotors for superior thermal management. Zero evidence of bore scoring or chain tensioner fatigue. This is a turn-key, investment-grade driver\u2019s car with a flawless service pedigree.",
